{"parse":{"title":"Valore (company)","pageid":11254342,"revid":852943334,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn org\">Valore</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"logo\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Valore-Logo.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Valore-Logo.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Valore-Logo.png/220px-Valore-Logo.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"47\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3e/Valore-Logo.png 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"320\" data-file-height=\"68\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Founded</th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n2005<span class=\"noprint\">&#59;&#32;13&#160;years ago</span><span style=\"display:none\">&#160;(<span class=\"bday dtstart published updated\">2005</span>)</span> (as SimpleTuition)<br />January&#160;2015<span style=\"display:none\">&#160;(<span class=\"bday dtstart published updated\">2015-01</span>)</span> (as Valore)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Headquarters</th><td class=\"label\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Boston\" title=\"Boston\">Boston</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Massachusetts\" title=\"Massachusetts\">Massachusetts</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/United_States\" title=\"United States\">U.S.</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Key people</div></th><td class=\"agent\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\nGeoffrey Willison <a href=\"/wiki/CEO\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"CEO\">CEO</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Parent_company\" title=\"Parent company\">Parent</a></th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Follett_Corporation\" title=\"Follett Corporation\">Follett</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Website</th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<span class=\"url\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.valore.com/\">www<wbr />.valore<wbr />.com</a></span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Valore</b> is an American company that provides an online textbook marketplace and open-source college textbooks that is based in <a href=\"/wiki/Boston\" title=\"Boston\">Boston</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TNM7April_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TNM7April-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Services_provided\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Services provided</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Valore_(company)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Valore, Inc. (formerly SimpleTuition, Inc.), is the Boston-based parent company of ValoreBooks,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> an online textbook marketplace, and <a href=\"/wiki/Boundless_(company)\" title=\"Boundless (company)\">Boundless</a>, a provider of openly licensed digital courseware.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The company was founded in 2005 with the launch of its first product, SimpleTuition, an online student loan comparison engine. The SimpleTuition product is now operated by Lending Tree. The company has launched a number of additional products including SmarterBucks, a rewards program that helps pay down any student loan. SmarterBucks was sold to Gradifi in 2015.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In 2012, to address the high cost of textbooks, the company acquired ValoreBooks \u2014 an online marketplace whose tagline claims that it saves students up to 90% on the cost of textbooks. In 2015, the company acquired Boundless, which offers affordable digital textbook replacements leveraging openly licensed content.\n</p><p>The name Valore means value in Italian.\n</p><p>Valore was venture-backed, and investors<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> included <a href=\"/wiki/Atlas_Venture\" title=\"Atlas Venture\">Atlas Venture</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Flybridge_Capital_Partners\" title=\"Flybridge Capital Partners\">Flybridge Capital Partners</a> and North Hill Ventures. Valore was acquired by <a href=\"/wiki/Follett_Corporation\" title=\"Follett Corporation\">Follett</a> in 2016.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Services_provided\">Services provided</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Valore_(company)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Services provided\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Valore, Inc. currently provides the following services:\n</p>\n<ul><li>ValoreBooks student textbook <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.valorebooks.com/buy-textbooks\">purchase</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.valorebooks.com/rent-textbooks\">rental</a> marketplace:  Aggregates sellers of textbooks to allow students to find affordable prices on textbooks they need for the semester</li>\n<li>ValoreBooks student textbook <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.valorebooks.com/sell-textbooks\">sellback</a> marketplace: Aggregates buyers of textbooks to give students an instant quote on textbooks they want to sell back</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://pages.valorebooks.com/merchant-solutions\">ValoreBooks Merchant Solutions</a>: Programs designed to help campus bookstores and textbook retailers buy and sell more textbook inventory</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.boundless.com/\">Boundless</a> digital textbook alternative: Affordable, openly licensed content meant to replace traditional textbooks</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Valore_(company)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist columns references-column-width\" style=\"-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-TNM7April-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-TNM7April_1-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkingnewmedia.com/2015/04/07/valore-acquires-digital-textbook-publisher-boundless/\">\"Valore acquires digital textbook publisher Boundless\"</a>. 7 April 2015<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">8 April</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Valore+acquires+digital+textbook+publisher+Boundless&amp;rft.date=2015-04-07&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.talkingnewmedia.com%2F2015%2F04%2F07%2Fvalore-acquires-digital-textbook-publisher-boundless%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AValore+%28company%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><i>PR Newswire</i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/simpletuition-acquires-valorebooks-textbook-marketplace-169157496.html\">http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/simpletuition-acquires-valorebooks-textbook-marketplace-169157496.html</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=PR+Newswire&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fsimpletuition-acquires-valorebooks-textbook-marketplace-169157496.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AValore+%28company%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:100%\" class=\"error citation-comment\">Missing or empty <code style=\"color:inherit; border:inherit; padding:inherit;\">&#124;title=</code> (<a href=\"/wiki/Help:CS1_errors#citation_missing_title\" title=\"Help:CS1 errors\">help</a>)</span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">. PR Newswire <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"